{
  "stem": "7177.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was given-- and we just-- you cannot call it a highlight, but it was the worst time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was given a tandem bike.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was the chauffeur or the driver of the tandem bike with my sister in the back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we rode-- and Ali and Tima again, the same couple who had transported us once before, were transported us back almost to the-- to my hometown.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very close-- close to my hometown.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what that meant another 25 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Same-- we did not go back the same way, because Tima thought that we would be very, very safe.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was raining so hard, we would cross the pontoon bridge, and we didn't have to take the row boat, that was his opinion, that would go faster.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was so scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I hadn't been outdoors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I hadn't done a thing for a year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We did-- Ali was in front, and she had, let's say, for-- for-- she was on a regular bike.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then I came on the tandem bike with my sister, and Tima followed up in back of us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How I got across the bridge, I do not know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was so nervous, of course, because on both sides, in the little guard houses, were the Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we made it across, and we made it all the way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The 25 miles-- actually, excuse me, 25 kilometers, and we traveled-- and I remember we-- we went on roads that were, of course, not very much traveled on.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "By that time, it was Saturday evening, about 10 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But since it was raining so hard, there were not that many people on the street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember that Tima came close to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
